text: Julie Leprohon (born November 30, 1980) is a Canadian fencer. She was part of the team Canada épée team who finished fourth at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female épée fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Canada Category:Fencers at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Fencers at the 2007 Pan American Games Category:Fencers from Montreal Category:French Quebecers Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games medalists in fencing Category:Medalists at the 2007 Pan American Games
